{"tid":1073385,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"有冇人覺得重慶紅衣男孩單野好撚邪","createTime":"2019-03-22T15:44:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T06:21:05.000Z","uid":5995,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e1760b3e1d8ee138681de095ea2a1559dfd1ae51","tid":1073385,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T15:44:44.000Z","msg":"這一個13歲少年被發現時，雙手懸掛在屋樑上、穿著大紅色裙子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be243641f18c168b8448ec9ab14dac115549b476","tid":1073385,"uid":134438,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T15:47:34.000Z","msg":"有人話係用嚟去幫人續命"},{"pid":"5267958dbde30dfb7e8d631187cdb80a3b353577","tid":1073385,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T15:51:28.000Z","msg":"2009年11月5日，54歲的農民工匡紀錄從江北趕回巴南區東泉鎮雙星村高石坎，為了給住讀的兒子送錢，家裡正門側門緊閉，平時從來不開的後門卻虛掩著，從後門進去，眼前一幕讓他大驚失色，兒子身穿紅色花裙子，雙手雙腳，被身子結結實實地捆著，腳上還吊著，一個大秤砣，雙手，被掛在梁屋上，早已死亡，根據警方和法醫解剖記錄，孩子從頭部到腹部，都被線縫著，匡志軍遺體，額頭前有一個小孔和不重的，外傷大腿，雙手兩肋，雙腳裸部上方都有極深的淚痕，此外沒有任何傷口。"},{"pid":"bfb849e0c6ec25254bcae200861eab1396b40b58","tid":1073385,"uid":175896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T16:03:22.000Z","msg":"More"},{"pid":"f021c4c37ecaa5feb67888622d41b0313d7c2fa7","tid":1073385,"uid":5487,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T16:05:26.000Z","msg":"最癲係啲公安查唔到邊個做就話係自殺......"},{"pid":"9514393453291fbd5e5b3dcf34a78a17cc3dad69","tid":1073385,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T16:06:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59396cf224eeb737613310e4f9b5bf77c34050d4","tid":1073385,"uid":3465,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T16:08:08.000Z","msg":"安已不<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7212d234efe05b8eb29a863cce4f4f54886ab5a6","tid":1073385,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22