re":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:13:37.000Z","msg":"怪談好撚正<br />\n唔撚想完呀仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:15:50.000Z","msg":"完撚左10世啦<br />\n就係拍完紅衣之後無啦啦宣布以後都唔會再有怪談<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T16:28:11.000Z","msg":"傳聞係幫too simple 續命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04c49f9a640cc5f5992b927dcc7e8bd39dbcd75","tid":1073385,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59057b39cf157187a652ed716eabd0b25c95d651","tid":1073385,"uid":117276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"779a906b5d581649e8bff809dd1b9a61803a8590","tid":1073385,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cfe7965272d38527504fd249374d740bc7443569","tid":1073385,"uid":191469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:13:37.000Z","msg":"怪談好撚正<br />\n唔撚想完呀仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:15:50.000Z","msg":"完撚左10世啦<br />\n就係拍完紅衣之後無啦啦宣布以後都唔會再有怪談<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T16:28:11.000Z","msg":"傳聞係幫too simple 續命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T17:03:29.000Z","msg":"呢單野肯定係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />傳聞中好似有幾個又去著紅色衫嘅"},{"pid":"594f60d36fe8c14bee04faa9126d54e3c9315ed2","tid":1073385,"uid":61876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T23:33:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bbs.tianya.cn/m/post-funinfo-7253286-1.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbbs.tianya.cn%2Fm%2Fpost-funinfo-7253286-1.shtml&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD15FIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=147fba93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bbs.tianya.cn/m/post-funinfo-7253286-1.shtml</a><br />\n唔好介意大陸網睇一睇"},{"pid":"20a7924259d6b51358a6f50647014fcd910c6efa","tid":1073385,"uid":61876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T23:38:00.000Z","msg":"小男孩死的時候剛好是13歲零13天，再加上服裝穿著怪異、腳上還有秤砣。根據玄學知識來看，紅衣男孩頭頂有針眼很可能就是用來泄魂的，紅色的裙子是用來鎖魂的，腳上綁的秤砣是墜魂的。<br />\n<br />\n穿紅衣上梁死亡，這是將其魂魄打散，永不超生的死法。死者死亡時，身現金木水火土五行跡象，再選屬陰的數字13歲零13天，按理說，作案時間也應該是陰時，亥時可能最大。這樣狠毒的做法就是想既讓對方家斷後，且讓死者永不超生，死後魂魄盡散，不會找凶手麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n頭頂有針眼，而這個針眼起到的是泄魂用作蛤蟆續命的作用，根據茅山道術上面的記載，那針應該用屍油泡過九九八十一天。根據以上簡述，這是標準的養鬼術前半段。<br />\n<br />\n如果此後不久有人離奇暴斃,則必定與此事有關. 如果有人離奇暴斃之後再其他事發生,則此案難破,就算抓住人也未必是真凶. 如果此後風平浪靜,無人離奇死亡,那這件事就不那麼簡單了. 從最初2009年底重慶男孩離奇死亡，有人推斷還要有12個人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n而且從發生事情之後到現在，一共有莆田4人+天台5人+天台2人+電話亭遇害女孩1人正好12個人死亡，而且最開始的男孩和最後的一個女孩都是被弔死的。<br />\n<br />\n一個重慶男孩被發現於2009年11月5號，溺死4人莆田2010年2月4日，天台2010年2月18日至3月2號溺死7人、弔死1人<br />\n<br />\n電話亭小姑娘是3月1日離開莆田的，3月2日晚身亡。當天陰歷正月17。每年的農歷正月17日晚飯過後，人們就紛紛到埋葬自己的親人的墳地里去為一過世的親人&ldquo;送蠟&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n查萬年歷:重慶男孩，2009年11月5日被發現死亡，死時13歲13天，生日大概1996年10月23左右，丙子年屬鼠,五行屬水。<br />\n<br />\n電話亭小姑娘，出生於2005年8月18日，陰歷7月14日，中元節，也就是鬼節，乙酉年生肖屬雞，五行屬水 2人均五行屬水。"},{"pid":"5f715fbc93a393f2cf5167cc67ce7eff15c63283","tid":1073385,"uid":181318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T23:51:00.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"199f7c86d1c6927bcc7f4f7e18ae79496388ee05","tid":1073385,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T00:14:53.000Z","msg":"月經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5053ee8db655407b5bc4aadab1f1b387d02da8bc","tid":1073385,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T00:42:52.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"a04d9a5bcf2c8ee8e942d0178abefc2bb19a50af","tid":1073385,"uid":185142,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T00:45:47.000Z","msg":"呢d通常有高清圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw有冇片?"},{"pid":"88f8fe879f2f602ef5d82124fdf4d8549f793246","tid":1073385,"uid":35508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T02:32:45.000Z","msg":"唔介意殘體可以睇下 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/30835865/answer/51324256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F30835865%2Fanswer%2F51324256&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD15FIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=36c79eeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/30835865/answer/51324256</a>"},{"pid":"ac7d0325775884c4492e57a22d29402f0f290d2e","tid":1073385,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T02:40:26.000Z","msg":"有套電影就係拍衣個案件"},{"pid":"50bd6a8aa94efb5df4b26d1ec638856753ef3c7f","tid":1073385,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59057b39cf157187a652ed716eabd0b25c95d651","tid":1073385,"uid":117276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"779a906b5d581649e8bff809dd1b9a61803a8590","tid":1073385,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cfe7965272d38527504fd249374d740bc7443569","tid":1073385,"uid":191469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:13:37.000Z","msg":"怪談好撚正<br />\n唔撚想完呀仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:15:50.000Z","msg":"完撚左10世啦<br />\n就係拍完紅衣之後無啦啦宣布以後都唔會再有怪談<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T16:28:11.000Z","msg":"傳聞係幫too simple 續命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:15:02.000Z","msg":"Who is too simple<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}